            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"Web-based-design-and-analysis-tools-for-CRISPR-base-editing\"><a href=\"#Web-based-design-and-analysis-tools-for-CRISPR-base-editing\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Web-based design and analysis tools for CRISPR base editing\"></a><code>Web-based design and analysis tools for CRISPR base editing</code></h2><span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n\n",
